I have a yi sport camera, which is unfortunately out of support,
the company seems dead at this point,
the official android app won't install on recent android.

this script simply starts the live stream, no other feature are planned at this point.

usage:
deno run --allow-net=192.168.42.1:7878 yi.ts

then use your favorite player to play
rtsp://192.168.42.1/live

note:
for mpv, you'll need --rtsp-transport=udp (or lavf), since it defaults to tcp

ref: https://github.com/deltaflyer4747/Xiaomi_Yi/blob/master/Standalone_scripts/Camera_video_stream.py